    "sr": false,
    "shortDescription": "<p>This spell functions like @Compendium[pf1.spells.ik9u3eel5vfwrtb5]{Grease}, except as noted here. When you use this spell to cover a solid surface with slippery <em>grease</em>, the 10-foot squares must form a continuous area, each part of which must be within the spell's range. When you use this spell to create a greasy coating on items, no two of the targeted items can be more than 30 feet apart. You cannot target both items and surfaces with a single casting of this spell.</p>"
